  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Launch a multi-partner call on Zica, targetting its social impacts through training, research and instititional development, responding to in - country priorities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Produce relevant applied research to respond to Zika&#xB4;s social impacts by generating training courses, improved protocols, stronger networks and collaborative platforms for learining and prevention of further impacs. Stiluate the construction of networks across 5 FAPS (research foundations from the states of Pernambuco, Cear&#xE1;, Distrito Federal, Para&#xED;ba e Alagoas)  and the Funda&#xE7;ao Oswaldo Cruz from the Ministry of Health.</narrative>
  </description>
